  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaor2_yanbaoPPT_1517_2",
    "text": "Employers have invested unprecedented resources in employee mental health and well-being. With burnout at all-time highs, leaders wonder if they can make a difference. Our research suggests they can.",
